article.description: — Trenton Massner had 25 points in Western Illinois' 90-72 victory over UT Rio Grande Valley on Saturday night.
article.headline: Western Illinois knocks off UT Rio Grande Valley 90-72
article.linkText: Western Illinois knocks off UT Rio Grande Valley 90-72
article.story: MACOMB, Ill. -- — Trenton Massner had 25 points in Western Illinois' 90-72 victory over UT Rio Grande Valley on Saturday night. Massner added six assists and three steals for the Leathernecks (4-4). Jesiah West added 18 points, five rebounds and three steals. Vuk Stevanic had 15 points. The Vaqueros (5-4) were led by Justin Johnson, who posted 21 points. Will Johnston added 17 points and C.J. Jackson also had 12. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
